OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FA woman who provides social media
OL,7,Fupdates for a rail company has spoken
OL,8,Fout about the abuse she has suffered
OL,9,Fat the hands of angry customers.
OL,11,FVictoria, who didn't want to give her
OL,12,Flast name, is part of a designated
OL,13,Fteam set up to help with online
OL,14,Fenquiries for Northern Rail.
OL,16,FShe has been in the job for eight
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,FShe told ITV News: "If you comment on
OL,20,Fa post or send a message it comes (to
OL,21,Fus). We see everything.
