OL,6,F''I honestly couldn't count how many
OL,7,Ftimes I've been told to kill myself.
OL,9,F''I have had someone track down what
OL,10,Fbuilding I was in at the time and say
OL,11,Fthat they're outside, they're waiting
OL,12,Fand they're going to attack me when I
OL,13,Fget outside.''
OL,15,FOne recent message directed towards
OL,16,FNorthern on social media, shown to ITV
OL,17,FNews, read: "Hope you get cancer and
OL,18,Fyour kids watch you die."
