OL,3,C'Hope you get cancer': The abuse aimed
OL,4,Cat rail company social team
OL,6,FJon Ellis-Fleming, from Hull, told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "I've had threats against my
OL,8,Flife, I've had threats against my
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,F"There are times when I worry about
OL,12,Ftaking my kids out. That's when it
OL,13,Fbecomes a concern for me. When my
OL,14,Ffamily, who are vulnerable, come out
OL,15,Fonto the railway."
OL,17,FHe previously worked as a travel
OL,18,Fsafety officer for Northern. He said:
OL,19,F"This (body camera) got activated on
OL,20,Fevery shift without fail.
