OL,6,F"I got an emergency call to get to
OL,7,Fdown to Ilkley as a guard had been
OL,8,Fassaulted and chased into the mess
OL,9,Froom. He had to barricade himself in
OL,10,Fwhile they were trying to kick the
OL,11,Fdoor in.''
OL,13,FNorthern has been under government
OL,14,Fcontrol in 2020, after the previous
OL,15,Foperator was stripped of its franchise
OL,16,Fdue to ongoing poor service.
