OL,6,FHe said: "We don't always get it right
OL,7,Fand we apologise for that. But there's
OL,8,Fnothing that can excuse that kind of
OL,9,Fbehaviour to our staff.
OL,11,F"Please recall that this could be a
OL,12,Ffamily member. It's not their fault.
OL,13,FThey are trying to help."
